I"	<p><strong>Huge monstrosity, chaotic evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 17 (natural armor)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 172 (15d12+75)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 20 ft., swim 40 ft.</p>

